org.apache.flink.types

接口 CopyableValue<T>

  • 所有超级接口:
    IOReadableWritable, java.io.Serializable, Value
    所有已知子接口:
    ValueArray<T>
    所有已知实现类:
    BooleanValue, ByteValue, ByteValueArray, CharValue, CharValueArray, DoubleValue, DoubleValueArray, FloatValue, FloatValueArray, IntValue, IntValueArray, LongValue, LongValueArray, LongValueWithProperHashCode, NullValue, NullValueArray, Record, ShortValue, ShortValueArray, StringValue, StringValueArray

    @Public
public interface CopyableValue<T>
extends Value
    Interface to be implemented by basic types that support to be copied efficiently.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法

      Gets the length of the data type when it is serialized, in bytes.

      • 从接口继承的方法 org.apache.flink.core.io.IOReadableWritable

    • 方法详细资料

      • getBinaryLength

        int getBinaryLength()
        Gets the length of the data type when it is serialized, in bytes.
        返回:
        The length of the data type, or -1, if variable length.

      • copyTo

        void copyTo(T target)
        Performs a deep copy of this object into the target instance.
        参数:
        target - Object to copy into.

      • copy

        T copy()
        Performs a deep copy of this object into a new instance. This method is useful for generic user-defined functions to clone a CopyableValue when storing multiple objects. With object reuse a deep copy must be created and type erasure prevents calling new.
        返回:
        New object with copied fields.

      • copy

        void copy(DataInputView source,
          DataOutputView target)
   throws java.io.IOException
        Copies the next serialized instance from source to target. This method is equivalent to calling IOReadableWritable.read(DataInputView) followed by IOReadableWritable.write(DataOutputView) but does not require intermediate deserialization.
        参数:
        source - Data source for serialized instance.
        target - Data target for serialized instance.
        抛出:
        java.io.IOException
        另请参阅:
        IOReadableWritable
